{"tid":1174770,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【沙中線】禮頓指無施工記錄表不代表無監督","createTime":"2019-05-28T05:37:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-28T17:29:37.000Z","uid":9812,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"560e1236b26c7057e7470d45b5236fe461c9d813","tid":1174770,"uid":9812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T05:37:46.000Z","msg":"沙中綫調查委員會聆訊，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">禮頓陳詞指施工記錄表格找不到，不代表不見了，禮頓人員是因為太忙，沒有交表格，並不代表沒有做好監督</span></span></strong>。 <br />\n<br />\n聆訊第二日，代表禮頓資深大律師石永泰緊接政府代表律師陳詞。早前扎鐵的分判商永光，陳詞指鋼筋和螺絲帽接駁不到，警告過禮頓，但對方沒有理會。 <br />\n<br />\n石永泰指留意到供詞，認為不太清晰，遲一點再探討是否真確，但引述禮頓的證人在施工期間沒有聽到工人指扭鋼筋有困難，又指禮頓看上去鋼筋接駁不好，是永光沒有做好。 <br />\n<br />\n車站有施工記錄不見了，北面隧道多達七成三簡稱 RISC 表格不知所蹤，石永泰指找不到不代表不見了，禮頓人員坦白承認是太忙，所以沒有交，委員會可以評斷禮頓管理夠不夠好，但禮頓的立場是沒有交表格，不代表沒有做好監督，亦不代表禮頓未做好檢查便落石屎，強調每個關鍵點都有檢查。 <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">至於南、北面隧道，與列車停放處擅改施工方法，石永泰解釋兩種接駁方式分別是用螺絲帽和鋼筋搭接，他指沒有證據顯示哪一種更好，獲批准的圖則亦沒有說明用哪種方法，最終用了螺絲帽是細節問題，不影響安全，認為不需要屋宇署批准。</span></strong> <br />\n<br />\n代表政府的大律師周偉倫指，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">港鐵檢測了紅磡站二百二十五個鋼筋樣本，六成八合格，有三十九條、約一成七鋼筋扭入螺絲帽少於三十七毫米、不達標，另外約有八枝沒有接駁</span></strong>，港鐵正分析車站結構，星期五向政府提交初步報告。<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/549422/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E7%A6%AE%E9%A0%93%E6%8C%87%E7%84%A1%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E8%A8%98%E9%8C%84%E8%A1%A8%E4%B8%8D%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E7%84%A1%E7%9B%A3%E7%9D%A3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F549422%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E7%25A6%25AE%25E9%25A0%2593%25E6%258C%2587%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%2596%25BD%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E8%25A8%2598%25E9%258C%2584%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E4%25B8%258D%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%259B%25A3%25E7%259D%25A3&d=4a077UaaKOqSfaiyS2iiQZB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=c7485da9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F549422%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E7%25A6%25AE%25E9%25A0%2593%25E6%258C%2587%25E7%2584%25A1%25E6%2596%25BD%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E8%25A8%2598%25E9%258C%2584%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E4%25B8%258D%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E7%2584%25A1%25E7%259B%25A3%25E7%259D%25A3&h=380c629b\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/549422/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E7%A6%AE%E9%A0%93%E6%8C%87%E7%84%A1%E6%96%BD%E5%B7%A5%E8%A8%98%E9%8C%84%E8%A1%A8%E4%B8%8D%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E7%84%A1%E7%9B%A3%E7%9D%A3</a>"},{"pid":"a9b8d23b4098383c14e1f470df5191999d641a56","tid":1174770,"uid":9812,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T05:38:08.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你試下一般打工仔做撚完野比人地check，得 68%合格<br />\n問你有無打卡你話太忙無打，你睇下你老細炒唔撚炒鳩你魷魚？</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"b6c5aa885d1f5be13745337adc2e12a03a67269e","tid":1174770,"uid":9812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T05:39:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9171b0563a1bc1e7ee62c1c0d3162d0b9b75b8e","tid":1174770,"uid":9812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T05:43:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9204bc8a0c7ee2b8824a69210960f1f04d6d3a7a","tid":1174770,"uid":254183,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T05:45:37.000Z","msg":"施工記錄表格找不